# GRE (RFC 2784 + RFC 2890 key/sequence) over IPv4, flags K+S, protocol type 0x6558 (Transparent
# Ethernet Bridging), Key 0x0000007b, Sequence 0x00000001 — tunneling a full inner Ethernet frame,
# which recurses via EthernetII (guarded to TEB). Exercises the optional Key + Sequence Number fields.
# source: standard GRE header + a real inner eth frame emitted via a raw IPPROTO_GRE socket on a
# debian:12 container's ethernet lo, captured with tcpdump.
